658117028, \"rank\": 9.341891186491086e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"hopes\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 164}, {\"ngram\": \"the final round\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"your help\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This talented group of surfers will be the first-ever American Samoa surfing team to participate in the Olympics, and they are ready to showcase their exceptional skills and dedication on the international stage.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This talented group\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"team\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"their exceptional skills\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"the international stage\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To prepare for the Olympics, the team will be heading to Puerto Rico for intensive training and competition.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9999997383602364, \"rank\": 1.6194569290485756e-07, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"intensive training\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But participating in the Olympics requires significant financial support, and they are reaching out to generous sponsors to fulfill their dream of representing American Samoa.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999267502089, \"rank\": 6.781683646791636e-08, \"text\": \"American Samoa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Samoa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"significant financial support\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"generous sponsors\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"their dream\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your sponsorship will not only help these surfers achieve their dreams but also promote American Samoa as a vibrant and talented surfing destination.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999267502089, \"rank\": 6.781683646791636e-08, \"text\": \"American Samoa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Samoa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your sponsorship\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"these surfers\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"their dreams\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"a vibrant and talented surfing destination\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In return, the team is offering promotional opportunities, including logo placement on team uniforms, acknowledgment on social media platforms, and recognition at local events.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"return\", \"from\": 922, \"to\":